{"title":"fix(remediation): increase mem-load container memory limit to prevent OOMKilled restarts","body":"Root cause: The mem-load container's memory limit (32Mi) is insufficient for the stress command which attempts to allocate 50M of memory, causing OOMKilled restarts.

Evidence: Back-off restarting failed container mem-load in pod vigil-app-66f84484b8-hvkcg_default(babf0708-13c2-48c8-8823-27d7167ee69a)

Fix: Increased mem-load container memory limit from 32Mi to 64Mi in Deployment/vigil-app."}
